# Sentiment Analysis Web Application

## Project Overview

This project is an end-to-end AI application that predicts the sentiment of user-entered text.

The application classifies text into:

- 😊 Positive
- 😐 Neutral
- 😞 Negative

## Technologies

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- NLTK
- FastAPI
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Project Structure

- Dataset
- Model Training
- FastAPI Backend
- Frontend
- Deployment